Package: StablePopulation
Title: Calculates Alpha for a Stable Population
Version: 1.0.2
Authors@R: person(given = "David", family = "Palacios Morales", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "dpmorales@ubu.es", comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0008-5412-8997"))
Author: David Palacios Morales [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0009-0008-5412-8997>)
Maintainer: David Palacios Morales <dpmorales@ubu.es>
Description: Provides tools to calculate the alpha parameter of the Weibull distribution, given beta and the age-specific fertility of a species, so that the population remains stable and stationary.
